updated on 2015-12-11

copy your Mi band SQLite database file to the current working directiory of R. You can find the database file in \Data\Data\com.xiaomi.hm.health\Databases\origin_db using RExplorer(for android). To access that file, you need root permission. The database file's name should remain "origin_db" and in the working directiory of R. Then just run the script, it will automatically plot total sleep duration, deep sleep duration and steps trend (using lm) to png files.

reference:
http://www.miui.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=2497413&page=1

安卓手机使用RE管理器（需ROOT权限）将小米手环的数据库文件导出，文件目录为\Data\Data\com.xiaomi.hm.health\Databases\origin_db，将文件放置于R的工作路径，文件名不得修改。运行R脚本，将会得到睡眠总时间，深度睡眠时间和步数的趋势图（使用线性模型）。
参考：
http://www.miui.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=2497413&page=1
